						               													<description>You will play as one of the survivors of the ill-fated Oceanic flight 815 which crash-landed on an island somewhere in the Pacific Ocean. You must go exploring with other survivors, visiting certain locations in order to discover answers to the many questions which surround the mysterious island.&amp;#10;Each time a player gains Answers Counters, the Story track will advance. When this track reaches the end, the game is over and the player with the highest value of Answers counters is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;LOST The Answers is a fun, Print and Play, Card Game (which uses a board) for 2 &amp;ndash; 5 players. You can get all the files needed to produce the game for FREE from http://mmboardgames.page.tl/MM-Board-Games.htm&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This is a revamp (using several brand new elements) of our old LOST Card Game, and brings things right up to date including events from Season 4 of the show.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;LOST is a copyrighted property. This is an unauthorized, unofficial game produced merely for the entertainment of fans and is non-profit making. This game is completely FREE for you to download, print and play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
